data.description: Welcome to 9310 Rhode Island Avenue. This property is poised for maximum returns and represents an excellent investment opportunity. This deal is in the heart of College Park, in close proximity to the University, all commuter routes and amenities. A perfect location for equity upside and recurring income. With 8 bedrooms and large common areas, plus a huge bonus room for office or entertainment area, this home is well suited for an entire family, or bedroom rentals.  Ultimately dynamic, the house is set up with full floor privacy measures and working spaces. There is ample parking, on street, driveway and detached garage! This home will benefit immensely from simple paint and flooring, kitchen and bathrooms are already beautifully renovated.  This is one you can't afford to miss, come to appreciate your vision here, schedule an exclusive property tour today!
